    "body": "I have a very similar problem, on macOS with bash 5.2.37 (from MacPorts). With just a normal terminal in iTerm, everything is fine. But once I open zellij, the prompt is stuck in all panes, even new ones. `starship explain` correctly reports the current cwd, but the prompt doesn't. But once I `bash -l`, the prompt is back responding in the new bash process.\n\nI pretty much emptied my `.bash_profile`/`.bashrc` with no difference. Not sure if it's a similar issue to this one, and whether it's related to starship or zellij.",
